Nollywood rising star Vicky Nwogu has admitted to having a brief but intense infatuation for filmmaker and star actor Ramsey Nouah. In a recent chat with The Nation, Vicky revealed Nouah as her sole crush in the Nigerian film industry.   Paul, CeeCee Oniya speak on music exploits     MTN Foundation tells new story with Ibiom: When Doves Fly     Yung6ix plans collaboration with Wyclef   “Ramsey Nouah aka Richard Williams. We all saw how Ramsey Nouah sprinkled some young zaddy hotness on our screens as Richard Williams. Please don’t get me started,” Vicky adduced to explain her claims. On how she has coped with advances from men, who might flock around her as a result of her fame and popularity, Vicky said there’s nothing out of ordinary about it. “It is natural for men to come to women. It is up to the lady to accept or refuse. There is nothing out of the ordinary. And over the course of my journey, I have been able to make good friends who happen to be male and have helped me grow in different parts of my life.”